PrecisAppointment of a TEMPORARY ADMINISTRATOR, namely the Hon. A. Kerr Twaddle, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Manitoba, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of MANITOBA over the course of a seven-day period in March, 1992 (17th-23rd).
